He does expert repairs and teaches a bicycle mechanics course.

He is only open part-time. Usually from around 2:00 to 6:00 PM M-F and noon or 1:00 to 5:00 on Saturday. If time is tight call first to make sure he's open.

People bring their bikes back to Bruce from all over the country because he can strighten bent forks frames and wheels that other shops would just toss out. So if a shop tells you your favorite bike is hopeless, see Brice before you give up hope!
